        {
            "title": "韓股單日暴跌6%領跌亞太，日經險守64000點關口！",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\" data-component=\"blocks\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"韓股單日暴跌6%領跌亞太，日經險守64000點關口！\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/lo/mysterio/api/5d8bbf3b003e87927e99e38408c45766e1c3f8d37c92b1591a813fc0f55aef28/lightyear_networkapi/resizefill_w960;quality_80;format_webp/https:%2F%2Fcontent-media.investing.com%2Fnews%2FLYNXMPEB1H0YB_M.jpg\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">韓股單日暴跌6%領跌亞太，日經險守64000點關口！</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>Investing.com -</strong>周五，7月24日，韓國KOSPI指數7月24日單日重挫6.12%，報6662.37點，成為亞太主要市場中跌幅最慘烈的指數，成交量高達2.48億手，賣壓貫穿全天。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日經225指數同日下跌2187.69點，跌幅3.29%，盤中低點一度觸及64215.29點。日本股市當前所處價位已位於52周區間下半段，52周高點為72831.73點，而52周低點報39850.52點。與韓國市場類似，日經225全天均承壓下行，顯示區域性拋售壓力並非局限于單一市場。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-9d6ba8a2-b35c-3bcd-9fa7-b4c27873694e-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">香港恒生指數午盤收報24891.84點，較前一交易日下跌318.97點，跌幅1.27%。盤中高點僅觸及25031.34點，未能有效突破，反映多頭動能有限。恒生指數52周低點為22518點，當前位置仍在低點上方約10%，但距52周高點28056.1點仍有相當差距。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">A股同步走弱，上證綜合指數低開低走跌超1%，深成指跌1.77%，創業板指跌1.78%。量能再度萎縮，滬深兩市半日成交額1.23萬億元，較上個交易日縮量2306億元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">相較於亞太市場的全線回檔，美股期貨在亞太交易時段整體表現平穩，方向信號分化。標普500指數期貨（ESU26）小幅走弱，截至數據採集時報7442.75點，微跌0.03%；道瓊斯30指數期貨（YMU26）則微升0.05%，報51921點。兩者波動均屬統計意義上的噪音，未對亞太市場下行形成明顯對沖信號。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此次亞太市場集體回檔的具體催化因素有待厘清，韓國市場的異常放量下跌尤為值得追蹤。投資者需關注後續是否有宏觀經濟數據公佈、區域地緣政治動態，或外資資金流向的進一步變化，這些因素將決定此輪調整是短期技術回檔還是更具持續性的趨勢轉變。美股正式收市後的表現及本周美國經濟數據動向，將為亞太市場下一個交易日提供重要參考。</p><blockquote class=\"border-pebble mx-5 my-7.5 border-l-2 pl-5 italic\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><strong>七月限時開搶！InvestingPro 4折到手，AI選股名單即刻用，跑贏標普500近3倍，全年冇更平，錯過就走寶！</strong><a data-yga='{\"yInteractivityType\":\"0\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yLinkText\":\"即刻點擊訂閱\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:即刻點擊訂閱;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;\" href=\"https://hk.investing.com/pro/pricing?utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_campaign=yahoo-hk\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em>即刻點擊訂閱</em></strong></a><strong>！</strong></p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/lo/mysterio/api/46314871482a85c6404b33f2de2399115db933e80afc78ffa09d83359bd74a52/lightyear_networkapi/resizefill_w960;quality_80;format_webp/https:%2F%2Fcontent-media.investing.com%2Fhk%2Fcontent%2F3a9212144287f73d2f21c68e0fe7b1dd.png\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure></blockquote></div>",
